Class Minimal

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.tracks.Minimal

  • public class Minimal
extends java.lang.Object
    Minimal track reports.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketTrackMinimal structure in "SPxPackets.h".
